        text: "' FSOUND_DSP_PRIORITIES"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' These default priorities are used by FMOD internal system DSP units.  They describe the"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' position of the DSP chain, and the order of how audio processing is executed."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' You can actually through the use of FSOUND_DSP_GetxxxUnit (where xxx is the name of the DSP"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "' unit), disable or even change the priority of a DSP unit."
