      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'FSOUND_SPEAKERMODES"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'These are speaker types defined for use with the FSOUND_SetSpeakerMode command."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Note - Only reliably works with FSOUND_OUTPUT_DSOUND or FSOUND_OUTPUT_XBOX output modes.  Other output modes will only"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'interpret FSOUND_SPEAKERMODE_MONO and set everything else to be stereo."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'Using either DolbyDigital or DTS will use whatever 5.1 digital mode is available if destination hardware is unsure."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
