        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'/* =================== */"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'/* FX functions.       */"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'/* =================== */"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: Whitespace
        text: " "
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   Functions to control DX8 only effects processing."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   - FX enabled samples can only be played once at a time, not multiple times at once."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   - Sounds have to be created with FSOUND_HW2D or FSOUND_HW3D for this to work."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   - FSOUND_INIT_ENABLESYSTEMCHANNELFX can be used to apply hardware effect processing to the"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     global mixed output of FMOD's software channels."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   - FSOUND_FX_Enable returns an FX handle that you can use to alter fx parameters."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   - FSOUND_FX_Enable can be called multiple times in a row, even on the same FX type,"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'     it will return a unique handle for each FX."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   - FSOUND_FX_Enable cannot be called if the sound is playing or locked."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: EndOfLineComment
        text: "'   - FSOUND_FX_Disable must be called to reset/clear the FX from a channel."
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
      - kind: Newline
        text: "\n"
